## About


<img src="images/clinton.jpg" style="width:25%">

Amanda Nagle is an MPH Candidate in the Population and Family Health department of the Mailman School of Public Health. She is pursuing a certificate in Sexuality, Sexual, and Reproductive Health.

She lives in Huntsville, Alabama and loves baking, biking, and books.
